user.biography: Kentucky Fried Chicken. Founded by The Colonel. Practitioners of The Hard Way. Purveyors of the World's Best Chicken.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Kentucky Fried Chicken on September 15, 2021 tagging @kfcfoundation. May be an image of 3 people, people standing and road.

node.text: There are very few things fried chicken can’t fix (we’re working on it), so until we figure that out, we have the KFC Foundation to help communities who need more than a full stomach. The Kentucky Fried Wishes program granted $10,000 to 11 different non-profit organizations nationwide, a combined total of $110,000, to complete projects on their wish lists and strengthen the communities that we’re so proud to be a part of. To see the full list of this year’s grant recipients visit www.KFC.com/newsroom. @kfcfoundation
